headline: Texas Instruments Reports Earnings Today. China Is a Big Question for the Stock.
summary: Texas Instruments  will report its earnings after the close on Tuesday.  It is the first major semiconductor company to report in this earnings season.  The analyst consensus is for Texas Instruments to report revenue of $4.65 billion for the third quarter, with adjusted earnings per share of $1.49.
